Leading retailer of luxury goods, Polo Limited, has introduced IWC Schaffhausen, makers of Swiss timepieces, into the Nigerian market.
 
In a statement, Executive Director of Polo Limited, Jennifer Obayuwana, commended IWC for its “progressive outlook, which has allowed the brand to continually re-invent.
  
She added: “IWC has created ladies’ watch models regularly since the late 1870s, one of which, is the Da Vinci Lady Chronograph.  The IWC brand is a promise of durability, reliability and value for money. 